readable.content: A brown dog is running in the snow with a smaller black dog running behind it . A large brown dog and small black dog walk on the snow . A little black dog and a large brown dog are out in the snow . Two dogs , a big dog and a small dog , run in the snow . Two dogs are standing in snow , the smaller one barking at the larger one .
